<br>
The glacier yeti caves (due east of the combine tunnel) 4-6 mobs will be there, 4 are static, 2 are wanderers, but may not be around due to warping. Still blue at 48, and yield pretty good xp and loot. Make this your XP 'anchor' spot.<br>
<br>
Once finished, while you're waiting for them to repop, run around outside the cave slaughtering everything that moves. Firepet was pretty effecient.<br>
<br>
At level 49, I got very good xp fighting just outside of KC.<br>
<br>
XP is GREAT in Scarlet Desert, and you will do well there with the 49 pets as well. <p>Naladini <BR>
Elementalist of the 51st Season-Stormhammer<BR>
