<br>
Pull up a fire pet, give him all the AC increasing items you can summon up, have the cleric buff him with his best. (If the Cleric has Donal's Vambraces then have him click valor on him.. cast on Celestial heal and click the vams and that's enough for your pet to solo 3 spiders at once!)<br>
<br>
Just make sure you do a small amount of damage to each one for full exp.<br>
<br>
While waiting for the web sites to respawn (Typicaly 3 spawn points per web site with 2 to 3 spiders in each.) just pull some Drolvargs, Giants and Cockatrices... be sure you and the Cleric hit the Bazaar and donate for a C3 and you can get from 48 to 49 before it wears off <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
There's also a rare spawn spider in the Spider webs called the Dread Widow. She's level 50 and you can take her easily if you and the Cleric are at 50% mana.. (Less mana if you have SoW and can aggro kite her.) She has about 5k hps but drops the Drachnid Thyxl. Nice stats and effect of Extended Range III.. NICE ITEM! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Hope this helps <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
(There are 3 sets of spider webs in Dreadlands, just look on EQAtlas for their locations.) and I've NEVER seen all 3 camped. <p><p> <img src="http://www.jackntracie.com/images/gojirax.jpg" border="0"></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujayteebushwacker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jaytee Bushwacker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Summoner Da'FoH</span><br>  Posts: 974<br> <font color=#333333>(9/6/02 7:27:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels4950.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: DP</span><hr size=1> Quick list of spots from my XP days...long long ago in a zone far far away...<br>
